commit.message:
Add support for big ints

This PR adds support for parsing Clojure's big integers.

Clojure:

```
user=> (clojure.edn/read-string "1N")
1N
```

Elisp:

```
(parseclj-parse-clojure "1N")
((:node-type . :root)
 (:position . 1)
 (:children
  ((:node-type . :number)
   (:position . 1)
   (:form . "1N")
   (:value . 1))))
```
